title: S16 Ep99: The Dark Djinn w/ Suffi Mystic Kamran Pasha
itunes:title: The Dark Djinn w/ Suffi Mystic Kamran Pasha
description:
Darkness Radio LIVE presents The Dark Djinn with Suffi Mystic Kamran Pasha

Dave welcomes special guest Kamran Pasha to discuss The Dark Djinn.What are these beings and what drives them? Kamran has investigated and confronted the Djinn and lived to share his experiences and knowledge about this misunderstood force that walks the space between our world and the next. Kamran is a Suffi Mystic and Hollywood Filmmaker.

Visit his site: www.KamranPasha.com

Visit his work: www.Patreon.com/KamranPasha
